When an extensions has a configurable list, the name of the root element of the list should always be written in plural.

The following parameter generates a root element called parameterList with a child element named parameterList.
{code}
	@Parameter
	private List<String> parameterslist;
{code}

The root name generated in the XSD should be parametersLists or parameters

